Write the method getInitials, which returns a String containing one uppercase initial per word in fullName, in the order the words appear. For example, if fullName is "john quincy adams", getInitials returns "JQA"; if fullName is "Alice", getInitials returns "A". Method getInitials must locate word boundaries using indexOf(" ") and substring, and must use firstLetter from part (a) to obtain each initial. Assume firstLetter works as specified, regardless of what you wrote in part (a). Complete method getInitials below.

